ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104irg1665702535447.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/irg1665702535447.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/irg1665702535447.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"irg1665702535447\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.Label</code> object provides access to selected properties of the label it represents. It is returned by the <code class=\"ph codeph\">getLabel</code> function of <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.Occurrence</code> and the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.Field</code> objects.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"irg1665702535447__section_w1249ab1b5b1_w1250ab1b5_w1251ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1048954e61\">\n                       \n Functions\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"irg1665702535447__table_d15218e1_d15219e1_d15220e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Data Manipulation Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"irg1665702535447__table_d15218e1_d15219e1_d15220e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Function</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"irg1665702535447__table_d15218e1_d15219e1_d15220e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"irg1665702535447__table_d15218e1_d15219e1_d15220e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"afv1665702535715.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/afv1665702535715.html\" title=\"Returns the text of the specified label.\">getValue()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"irg1665702535447__table_d15218e1_d15219e1_d15220e1__entry__2\">\n Sets the text of the label.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"irg1665702535447__table_d15218e1_d15219e1_d15220e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"izg1665702535563.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/izg1665702535563.html\" title=\"Sets the text of the specified field label.\">setValue()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"irg1665702535447__table_d15218e1_d15219e1_d15220e1__entry__2\">\n Returns the text of the label.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"irg1665702535447__section_w1252ab1b5b3_w1253ab1b5_w1254ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1048954e133\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"irg1665702535447__p_d127268e1_d127269e1_d127270e1\">The functions available on the Label data object make it possible to dynamically change the label of a field. The Label object is returned by the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getLabel</span> function on the Field and Occurrence data objects.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"irg1665702535447__section_sbw_jlv_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1048954e145\">Example: Setting the Label of a Field</h2>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104irg1665702535447_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"irg1665702535447__codeblock_zh3_bhv_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">var vInstance = uniface.getInstance(\"MY_DSP\");\nvar vEntity = vInstance.getEntity(\"ORDER.ACME\");\nvar vOcc = vEntity.getOccurrence(0);\nvar vField = vOcc.getField(\"CUSTOMER\");\n// Set the label of field CUSTOMER\nvar vLabel = vField.getLabel() // Same as vOcc.getLabel(\"CUSTOMER\")\nvLabel.setValue(\"Client: \")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ycv1665702535357.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getLabel()</a><p>Returns the uniface.Label object that represents the Field's label.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528668\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528668\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uniface.Label Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The uniface.Label object provides access to selected properties of the label it represents. It is returned by the getLabel function of uniface.Occurrence and the uniface.Field objects. Functions Table 1. Data Manipulation Functions Function Description getValue() Sets the text of the label. setValue() Returns the text of the label. Description The functions available on the Label data object make it possible to dynamically change the label of a field. The Label object is returned by the getLabel function on the Field and Occurrence data objects. Example: Setting the Label of a Field Explain this code var vInstance = uniface.getInstance(\"MY_DSP\"); var vEntity = vInstance.getEntity(\"ORDER.ACME\"); var vOcc = vEntity.getOccurrence(0); var vField = vOcc.getField(\"CUSTOMER\"); // Set the label of field CUSTOMER var vLabel = vField.getLabel() // Same as vOcc.getLabel(\"CUSTOMER\") vLabel.setValue(\"Client: \") Copy Related Links getLabel() Returns the uniface.Label object that represents the Field's label. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}